[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man seriously injured in attack in Knightswood, Glasgow

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 51-year-old man is in a serious condition after being attacked in the Knightswood area of Glasgow.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The assault happened in Rotherwood Avenue at about 17:00.
The man was taken to the Queen Elizabeth University Hospital with serious injuries. His condition has been described as "serious but stable".
Police have asked anyone with information to contact them.
